trans-unit.source: Enumerates <see cref="T:System.Windows.TextDecoration" /> items in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.TextDecoration" />.
trans-unit.target: 列舉 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TextDecoration" /> 中的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TextDecoration" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: Gets the current element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得集合中目前的項目。

trans-unit.source: The current <see cref="T:System.Windows.TextDecoration" /> in the collection.
Advances the enumerator to the next element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 將列舉值設為集合中的下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator successfully advanced to the next element; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果成功將列舉值設為下一個項目則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: This method also returns `false` if the enumerator has passed the final element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法也會傳回`false`如果列舉值超過最後一個項目的集合中。

trans-unit.source: Resets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 重設列舉值至初始位置，也就是集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: For a description of this members, see <see cref="P:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current" />.
trans-unit.target: 如需這個成員的說明，請參閱 <see cref="P:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current" />。

trans-unit.source: The current element in the collection.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是明確介面成員實作，

trans-unit.source: It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.TextDecorationCollection.Enumerator> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> interface.
trans-unit.target: 只有在 <xref:System.Windows.TextDecorationCollection.Enumerator> 執行個體轉換成 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> 介面時，才能使用這個成員。

trans-unit.source: For a description of this members, see <see cref="M:System.IDisposable.Dispose" />.
trans-unit.target: 如需這個成員的說明，請參閱 <see cref="M:System.IDisposable.Dispose" />。
